name: Alien Dawg
description: With a sour and pungent odor, Alien Dawg has a light, bitter taste and presents brilliant mind and body effects. Originating from Northern California and Afghanistan, Alien Dawg is a cross between Chem Dawg and Alien Technology with a THC content of up to 20%.
description2: Descending from Northern California and Afghanistan genetics, Alien Dawg is a cross between Chemdawg and Alien Technology with a THC content of up to 20%. With a sour and pungent odor, Alien Dawg has a light, bitter taste and presents brilliant mind and body effects.

name: Blue Dream
description: Blue Dream is a sativa hybrid originating from California and has the lineage of Blueberry and Haze. It was primarily bred to provide the intense couch-locking body high of indica and the immense cerebral effects of a sativa. It has achieved legendary status among west coast strains. The effect of this strain will immediately make the users feel the sativa based effects that are associated with its hybrid lineage. It is a great strain to use to unwind and relax your body from a long day. An hour later, the users may begin to feel the indica based effects of an intense body high. It is absolutely great to serve as a mood elevator for the ones suffering from anxiety, stress, insomnia, chronic or debilitating pain, and lack of appetite. The cons of this strain would be occasional bouts of dizziness and and paranoia along side the commonly found side effects of dry mouth and eyes.
description2: Blue Dream, a sativa-dominant hybrid originating in California, has achieved legendary status among West Coast strains. Crossing a Blueberry indica with the sativa Haze, Blue Dream balances full-body relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration. Novice and veteran consumers alike enjoy the level effects of Blue Dream, which ease you gently into a calm euphoria. Some Blue Dream phenotypes express a more indica-like look and feel, but the sativa-leaning variety remains most prevalent. With a sweet berry aroma redolent of its Blueberry parent, Blue Dream delivers swift symptom relief without heavy sedative effects. This makes Blue Dream a popular daytime medicine for patients treating pain, depression, nausea, and other ailments requiring a high THC strain.

name: Cold Creek Kush
description: A potent cross of the MK Ultra and Chem-91, Cold Creek Kush is an indica dominant hybrid strain which is bred by T.H. Seeds. One of the popular strains across the globe, Cold Creek Kush won 2nd Place at the 2010 High Times Cannabis Cup in the indica category. This strain has a flowering period of 9-10 weeks. The growers must have adqequate room to stretch out its limbs. Piney and sour, users will feel the fresh taste and balanced effect of this strain which is extremely relaxing without being too sleepy.
description2: Cold Creek Kush is an indica-dominant hybrid that crosses the powerful MK Ultra and fellow Colorado native Chemdawg 91. The work of T.H. Seeds, this strain nabbed 2nd place at the 2010 High Times Cannabis Cup in the indica category. Cold Creek Kush flowers at 9 to 11 weeks, but must have adequate room to stretch out its limbs. Piney and sour, users rave over its fresh taste and balanced effects, which are relaxing without being too sleepy.

name: Great White Shark
description: It's serious medicine with clinically-tested THC levels of 14.85% and CBD levels of just 0.22%. Most patients truly appreciate the sedative, analgesic effects of this marijuana strain. Great White Shark is one that is super potent and provides a very powerful narcotic effect. It is an effective strain for stimulating the appetite, relieving depression, migraines, and nausea. Great White Shark is a sativa strain with high levels of THC providing the patient with a psychoactive, energetic, mind-high.

name: Lemon Skunk
description: With a Lemon mother (which has been kept in Vegas for over 20 years) and a father hand-picked in Holland, you know you are getting a heavy hitter! Lemon Skunk is a sativa dominant, hybrid strain good for pain and stress. It's a cross between two Skunks with phenotypes chosen for their zesty lemon characteristics. As the name implies, it has the flavour of citrus.
description2: Lemon Skunk was conceived from two separate Skunk phenotypes that displayed exceptionally zesty lemon traits. The skunky, citrus flavor draws you in immediately, and the happy, energetic buzz will shake you out of any funk. DNA Genetics has developed Lemon Skunk as great strain for combating depression and stress.

name: Mango
description: If you want Mango to stay at an average size in an outdoor garden, allow only 3 weeks of vegetative time and transplant outdoors as late as July in Northern latitudes. Mango's parentage is part KC 33 and part Mango from a hippie fellow who grew it for 30 years, then let KC use it as a cross in 1991. Don't let Mangos slow start fool you - this variety will eventually rival the impressive size of many KC varieties, which are especially intended for outdoor grows.
description2: The Mango cannabis strain has been around since the early 1960s. In 1991, it was crossed with KC 33 to give us the current Mango strain. Its buds have been known to grow very large, about the size of a softball, and can be up to a foot and a half in length. The foliage turns to a deep red/purple color with a smell and taste of sweet mango. Mango takes 9 to 11 weeks to flower and has a THC content of 15-20%.

name: Pink Kush
description: Relaxation runs in Pink Kush's indica genes, promoting rest and stress relief without total sedation. Even for veteran consumers, the heaviness of this strain could be considered overpowering, and even small doses eliminate pain, insomnia, and appetite loss. Pink Kush (as legendary as its OG Kush relative) is an indica dominant hybrid with powerful body-focused effects. Growers have to wait 10-11 weeks for Pink Kush's flowering, but the large top-shelf yields are worth the wait.
description2: Pink Kush, as coveted as its OG Kush relative, is an indica-dominant hybrid with powerful body-focused effects. In its exceptional variations, pink hairs burst from bright green buds barely visible under a blanket of sugar-like trichomes, with traces of a sweet vanilla and candy perfume. The potency of this strain could be considered overpowering, and even small doses are known to eliminate pain, insomnia, and appetite loss. Growers have to wait 10 to 11 weeks for Pink Kush’s flowering, but high yields of top-shelf buds are worth the wait.

name: Shishkaberry
description: Shiskaberry's buds have a fruit and berry aroma and will be painted with shades of purple. Its initial head buzz is happy and good for finishing things up or being social, but once its indica side kicks in, lazy is the word. Shiskaberry, or ?Kish,? is an indica dominant hybrid that came about from crossing DJ Short Blueberry with an unknown Afghani strain. This plant will mature in 8 to 9 weeks and should yield a fairly high amount of flowers.
description2: Shishkaberry, or “Kish,” is an indica-dominant hybrid that came about from crossing DJ Short Blueberry with an unknown Afghani strain. This plant will mature in 8 to 9 weeks and should yield a fairly high amount of flowers. Shiskaberry’s buds have a fruit and berry aroma and will be painted with shades of purple. Its initial head buzz is happy and good for finishing things up or being social, but once its indica side kicks in, lazy is the word.

name: Super Skunk
description: This strain carries a very strong skunky smell and provides a pleasant high with a little body to it. Super Skunk was developed for skunk lovers.Sensi Seeds took original Skunk #1 and other Afghani indicas to create this fine plant.
description2: A predominantly indica variety, Super Skunk takes its robust flowers from its parent strain Skunk #1. By backcrossing the legendary Skunk with Afghani genetics, Sensi Seeds created a strain with dense, thick buds that are known to be extremely pungent with a surprisingly sweet taste. This strain produces a bold relaxing effect over the body and is a great answer for increased stress and body pains.

name: Tangerine Dream
description: While too much Tangerine Dream may leave you stuck on the couch, this strain was handcrafted to meet the demands of working medical patients. A strain for connoisseurs, Tangerine Dream is the hybrid daughter of G13 and Neville's breeder strain A5. Uplifting and euphoric, it provides users with mental clarity while deeply relaxing muscles. Tangerine Dream typically flowers in 8 to 10 weeks and features a citrusy aroma. Its ability to knock out pain while increasing energy is what makes this strain so special. This winner of the 2010 Cannabis Cup was created by the illustrious Barney's Farm.
description2: This winner of the 2010 Cannabis Cup was created by the illustrious Barney’s Farm. A strain for connoisseurs, Tangerine Dream is the hybrid daughter of G13, Afghani, and Neville's A5 Haze. Its ability to knock out pain while increasing energy is what makes Tangerine Dream so special. While too much Tangerine Dream may leave you stuck on the couch, this strain was handcrafted to meet the demands of working medical patients. Uplifting and euphoric, it provides users with mental clarity while deeply relaxing muscles. Tangerine Dream typically flowers in 8 to 10 weeks and features a citrusy aroma.

name: White Widow
description: One of the most famous strains in the world, White Widow is a balanced hybrid first bred in the Netherlands. A cross between Brazilian sativa landrace and resin heavy South Indian indica, it has been on the menu of many Dutch coffee shops. A relatively new strain which was developed in 1990s, the buds of this strain are covered in crystals giving it an almost sugary look. This strain provides the user with a buzz of euphoria and energy breakthroughs stimulating creativity and conversation. The genetics of this particular strain is known to have helped originate many other legendary strains though many harvesters prefer the original White Widow which has a flowering time of about 60 days indoors.
description2: Among the most famous strains worldwide is White Widow, a balanced hybrid first bred in the Netherlands by Green House Seeds. A cross between a Brazilian sativa landrace and a resin-heavy South Indian indica,  White Widow has blessed every Dutch coffee shop menu since its birth in the 1990s. Its buds are white with crystal resin, warning you of the potent effects to come. A powerful burst of euphoria and energy breaks through immediately, stimulating both conversation and creativity. White Widow’s genetics have given rise to many other legends like White Russian, White Rhino, and Blue Widow. Still, many growers prefer cultivation of the original White Widow, which flowers in about 60 days indoors.

name: Argyle
description: Argyle is an indica-dominant strain with a balanced THC-to-CBD ratio. Its verdant green buds are quite dense and are accented by orange hairs. The terpene myrcene is responsible for Argyle's earthy aroma.
description2: Argyle is a variety of Nordle grown by Canadian LP Tweed, Inc. The indica-dominant hybrid crosses Afghani and Sensi Star genetics. The resulting buds smell of garlic and herbs, like fresh cut chives but with a fruity aftertaste. With a 1:1 ratio of THC to CBD Argyle creates a mellow, calming buzz that is a great answer to body pains and muscle spasms.

name: Bakerstreet
description: The Bakerstreet cultivar is an indica-dominant THC strain. Its dense and deep green buds are highlighted with ochre-hued pistils and covered with trichomes. Terpinolene is the terpene which gives this strain its scent of juniper.
description2: Bakerstreet is a variety of Hindu Kush grown by Canadian LP Tweed. It is a pure indica with origins in the Hindu Kush mountain range. The subtle sweet and earthy sandalwood aroma of Bakerstreet induces a deep sense of calm that helps bring relief to those suffering pain, nausea, and stress disorders. Its heavy body effects make it a top strain to help you relax and unwind at the end of a long day.

name: Banana Split
description: Hanging out close to the middle, the banana split strain is a hybrid with a bit of indica dominence. It will hit you fast, and make you hungry. This strain is perfect for hanging out on the couch or some light productivity. Of course, as the name suggests, this strain will taste just like a dessert with a bit of a tangy after-taste. Expect to embrace happiness.
description2: Bred by Crockett Farms, Banana Split is a sativa-dominant cross of their famous Tangie and Banana Sherbert. Banana Split offers a clean level-headed high suitable for anyone looking to have a productive day. Growers can expect large buds with oversized frosty colas that host a Tangie-derived citrus aroma alongside sweet flavors from Banana Sherbet.

name: GSC
description: What happens when you mix OG Kush and Durban Poison? You get GSC or "Girl Scout Cookies." Don't let the friendly name fool you, this hybrid strain will send you flying into euphoria and relaxation. This award winning strain tastes sweet and earthy with a strong spicy aroma.
description2: GSC, formerly known as Girl Scout Cookies, is an OG Kush and Durban Poison hybrid cross whose reputation grew too large to stay within the borders of its California homeland. With a sweet and earthy aroma, GSC launches you to euphoria’s top floor where full-body relaxation meets a time-bending cerebral space. A little goes a long way with this hybrid, whose THC heights have won GSC numerous Cannabis Cup awards. Patients needing a strong dose of relief, however, may look to GSC for severe pain, nausea, and appetite loss. There are several different phenotypes of the GSC strain including Thin Mint and Platinum Cookies, which exhibit some variation in appearance and effect. Typically, however, GSC expresses its beauty in twisting green calyxes wrapped in purple leaves and fiery orange hairs. Patients and consumers looking to cultivate this cannabis staple themselves should wait 9 to 10 weeks for their indoor plants to finish flowering.

name: Moonbeam
description: If you're ready for bed, what better way to help you relax than a beam from the moon? The Moonbeam strain is an explosive indica that packs a lot of punch. We like to call this the "lullaby" strain as it will get you relaxed and feeling good. It will taste like a fruity tea - also the perfect flavour for bedtime!
description2: Grown by Canadian LP Leafs By Snoop, Moonbeam is an extremely potent indica strain with high THC content. Expect flavors to be fruity and sweety with earthy undertones. Consumers seek this strain for relief of insomnia and anxiety, as its potency can be a one-way ticket to an early bedtime.

name: Sunset
description: When it's not quite bed-time, a moderate indica might be your best bet. The Sunset strain is perfect for relaxing after a long day without leaving the planet or falling asleep right away. The flavour profile for Sunset is spicy with a smooth woody finish.
description2: Grown by Canadian LP Leafs By Snoop, Sunset is a THC powerhouse with heavily physical effects. Expect buds to be dark green in color with heavy trichome production. Flavors are earthy and spicy, bringing about euphorically sedative effects. Lovers of couchlock strains or any patients seeking relief from anxiety and/or pain should definitely give Sunset a try.

name: Ultra Sour
description: A hybrid with indica dominence, Ultra Sour combines MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel. This strain has been known to be perfect for vaping since its got a ton of THC and a fairly unique flavour. Expect this to be sweet and sour, with a underlying pine and earthy profile. Oh, almost forgot, Ultra Sour will make you REALLY HAPPY.
description2: Ultra Sour by THSeeds is a tart cross out of Amsterdam. This strain is the product of crossing MK Ultra and East Coast Sour Diesel, creating a sativa-dominant bud with uplifting stimulation and heady euphoria. Ultra Sour smells of pine and diesel, and its buds are deep green with rusty orange pistils. The potent mental effects can be a little daunting for inexperienced consumers, so mind your dosage. Enjoy Ultra Sour as a means to shrug off stress and enhance creativity.

description: We love 50. This strain has indica dominence, but is still a hybrid. It's been known to be "medium" strength, with moderate THC levels. 50 shouldn't make you feel drowsy, but will still let you relax your mind, body, and soul. When you finally do make it to bed, you'll be sure to get a good night's sleep. Sweet, with a touch of citrus and a bit of pine, this strain resembles a fine wine.
description2: A classic hybrid (with a 55:45 ratio of sativa to indica), 50 has strong THC potency. It is grown in Up CannabisÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s FiddlerÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Greenhouse in Niagara, Ont., where itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s hand-trimmed, sorted and hang-dried. Its terpene profile is highlighted by alpha-pinene (also found in resins of pine and other conifers, rosemary and sage), which gives it its strong piney, earthy aroma with woodsy undertones. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 1 g and 3.5 g packages.

name: Airplane Mode
description: Why is Airplane Mode so expensive? This strain is grown with great care - hand trimmed and hang dried. It's a medium potency indica that is perfect for the evenings and will leave you happy and relaxed. If you're not looking for a strain that will knock you out, this might be the perfect choice. The flavour isn't too strong, but you can expect to taste/smell flowers and trees.
description2: Airplane Mode from AltaVie is hand-trimmed and hang-dried. This indoor-grown indica-dominant strain has medium THC potency and a woody and earthy aroma created by the myrcene, beta-pinene and terpinolene in its terpene mix. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Balanced
description: MILD. This strain is suitable for beginners that are looking for a subtle and very tolerable high. It's an indica, but it won't leave you burnt out when it wears off. At the price, it is a good value for anyone looking to explore how legalized cannabis may be a new part of their lifestyle. Not recommended for highly experienced users that are looking for strong effects.
description2: This indica-dominant hybrid strain from Plain Packaging is greenhouse-grown and has very mild THC potency. Its green buds are accented by orange hairs, and its myrcene terpene profile (which is also present in hops and thyme) produces an earthy, clove-like aroma. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in various dried flower sizes.

name: Balanced Milled
description: MILD and MILLED. This strain is suitable for beginners that are looking for a subtle and very tolerable high - bonus: it's pre-grinded for your convenience. It's an indica, but it won't leave you burnt out when it wears off. At the price, it is a good value for anyone looking to explore how legalized cannabis may be a new part of their lifestyle. Not recommended for highly experienced users that are looking for strong effects.
description2: Plain PackagingÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s milled indica-dominant hybrid strain is greenhouse-grown and has very mild THC potency. This conveniently pre-ground flower is accented by orange hairs, and its myrcene terpene profile (which is also present in hops and thyme) produces an earthy, clove-like aroma. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in various dried flower sizes.

name: Cabaret
description: If you're a fan of day-drinking, you'll like Cabaret. This is a very strong sativa dominent strain that is hand-trimmed and hang dried. It's definitely a premium strain at the price, but it's packaged perfectly and might just be worth the price. Expect a lot of energy and uplifting feeling, suitable for a fun day off. It's been known to have a sweet, grapefruit flavour and a strong aroma. This strain is perfect for high-energy activities.
description2: Cabaret from Alta Vie is a sativa-dominant strain with a sweet aroma and hints of grapefruit, and very strong THC potency. It is grown, hand-trimmed and hang-dried indoors, and has a terpene mix that includes terpinolene for fruitiness. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Campfire
description: A hybrid strain with tons of aroma, Campfire offers mild potency but tons of CBD. What does that mean for you? Expect a body buzz without a headache. Most of the mental effects will be fairly minimal, but you will still be entitled to a bit of nostalgia. It's better suited for the evenings, but it can be enjoyed at any time since it won't knock you off balance. Lots of rich flowers as far as flavour and aroma goes without too much of an after-taste.
description2: Campfire from AltaVie is a hybrid strain that is grown, hand-trimmed and hang-dried indoors. Its terpene profile, consisting of myrcene, alpha- and beta-pinene, and guaiol, is what gives it its unique floral aroma. It has very mild THC potency and is available in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Casablanca
description: Casablanca is pretty strong stuff. It's not great for beginners unless you're looking for a really strong buzz. It's indica dominence makes it better for evening use or just before bed. It's not overly euphoric, but it will give you quite a bit of relaxation and have minimal side effects. The flavour profile is fairly mild with some citrus and a nice fresh aroma.
description2: Indica-dominant Casablanca from Edison is a bold indoor-grown and machine-trimmed strain featuring plush, rich forest green flowers with hints of orange, tightly woven buds and an earthy, fresh aroma from the alpha-pinene and myrcene in its terpene mix. It has strong THC potency and is available in four dried flower weights: 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g.

name: City Lights
description: City lights is potent, but also extremely calming. This indica strain packs a lot of THC, and won't require you to use a whole lot to get the job done. Expect an overall relaxing effect with a slight body buzz. Once your high wears off, this strain will likely put you right to bed as the increased potency can create a bit of burn-out. The taste isn't very strong, but you will get some spice and earthy notes on the tip of your tongue.
description2: Indica-dominant City Lights from Edison is a bold indoor-grown strain recognized by its lush bud structure and vibrant jade colour. Its freshness, earthiness and sweetness come from the myrcene and humulene in its terpene mix. It has very strong THC potency and is available in four dried flower weights: 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g.

name: Dreamweaver
description: Dreamweaver is more widely known as MK Ultra. This indica strain had a medium potency and a very fair price. Suited for late afternoon or evening use, you will feel calm and relaxed, and just a tad sleepy. The flavours aren't anything really exciting, just your typical earthy/piney notes but sometimes you might get a hint of citrus.
description2: Grown indoors in Paris, Ont., Dreamweaver is an indica strain that is comparable to MK Ultra.Ã‚ Its THC potency is medium, its aroma has been described as earthy and strong, and its flavour combines piney woods with hints of spice and vibrant citrus, thanks to the myrcene, humulene, nerolidol and limonene in its terpene profile. DreamweaverÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s dense green buds are covered in bright orange pistils, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available for purchase in dried flower form only.

name: Fantasy Island
description: Fantasy island is an indica that doesn't put you right to bed. Although it's known for being relaxing and calming, it can also make you feel a lot of happiness. In terms of strength, Goldilocks would probably call this strain "just right." The best part about Fantasy Island is the flavour profile: island inspired with berry, pumpkin, and a bit of sweetness.
description2: Fantasy Island from Synr.g is grown and hand-sorted in the Niagara Escarpment. The indica-dominated strain has medium THC potency and a complex taste because of the beta- and trans-caryophyllene, myrcene, limonene and alpha-pinene in its terpene mix. Fantasy Island is available pre-rolled and in three dried flower sizes.

name: Gather
description: It's the middle of the day, you want to get high but still want to be productive in the evening - if this sounds like you try Gather. This strain is sativa dominent with a medium potency. You'll likely zone out into whatever activity you're doing, but still feel extremely uplifted and energetic. Try this strain with #yoga on the beach or some #chores around the house. Fruit and herbs make this strain fun to exhale due to its subtle sweetness.
description2: Sun-grown in an eco-friendly greenhouse, Gather has medium THC potency and a musky aroma. The strainÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s buds are a vibrant green, and the myrcene and beta-pinene mix of its terpene profile give it an unmistakable muskiness. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available pre-rolled and in several dried flower weights.

name: Gems
description: A hybrid with a sativa dominence, Gems smokes as great as it looks. Medium-high from a strength perspective, this strain is great if you don't want to fall asleep when you sober up. Try this strain with #music or #movies for a fun and uplifting experience. Fruits and peppers make up the bulk of the flavour for Gems.
description2: Gems is a strong-trichome sativa-dominant flower that has medium THC potency. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s grown in Up CannabisÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s FiddlerÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Greenhouse in Niagara, Ont., where itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s hand-trimmed, sorted and hang-dried. Its buds are blanketed with white crystal-capped trichomes and vibrant orange hairs, and its terpene profile, highlighted by nerolidol (also found in citronella, ginger and orange peels), exudes a fruity aroma. Gems is available in 1 g and 3.5 g packages.

name: Houndstooth
description: A sativa hybrid that will wake you right up. Houndstooth is far from your bedtime strain of choice, as you'll feel both a cerebral and physical high. It is known to be medium/strong but still great for beginners as the effects can be somewhat mild. If you need a little #motivation or #focus, Houndstooth might just be perfect for you. Expect a sweet, citrus taste with a healthy dose of lemons.
description2: Greenhouse-grown Houndstooth from Tweed is a sativa-dominant strain with medium THC potency. Its buds have a purple hue and a complex aroma created by a terpene profile that includes myrcene (earthy), beta-caryophyllene (clove-like) and alpha-pinene (piney). ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in various dried flower sizes, capsules and pre-rolls.

name: La Strada
description: Sativa at its finest - La Strada offers a medium strength strain perfect for social settings. This strain will uplift and excite without being too overwhelming. It is known for a burn-out, so best used during late afternoons or early evenings. The flavour includes berries and tanginess while the aroma is sweet and fresh.
description2: Sativa-dominant La Strada from Edison is an indoor-grown and machine-trimmed strain with robust, dense, trichome-frosted green and orange flowers, a tangy, tart aroma and notes of freshly picked field berries created by the myrcene in its terpene mix. It has medium THC potency and is available in four dried flower weights: 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g.

name: Lola Montes
description: A body buzz in the evening is best achieved with Lola Montes. This indica strain is quite potent, offering a great body buzz and sleepy, calming effects. It doesn't create too much of an appetite and smokes very smooth. The earthy and fruity notes give it a great flavour and smell. This strain might not be best for beginners, but will be wildly enjoyed by moderate to heavy cannabis consumers.
description2: Lola Montes, from Edison, is an indica-dominant strain with very strong THC potency. This strain produces flowers with a tight, dense structure and a two-tone emerald hue, and its terpene profile includes beta-caryophyllene, guaiol, myrcene, bisabolol and humulene.

name: No. 301 Napali CBD
description: Body buzz anyone? The 301 Napali CBD strain achieves a magnificent euphoria followed by a sense of relaxation and stress-release. Technically, this is a hybrid strain but its unique in its low THC high CBD ratio. Expect a flavourful experience with pine and berry notes, with a strong earthy aroma.
description2: Haven St. grows and harvests No. 301 Napali CBD indoors as an irradiated whole flower, and then hand-trims and hang-dries the green and yellow buds. The alpha-pinene and limonene in its terpene profile give it its sweet, tropical flavour and earthy notes. Napali CBD has mild THC potency and comes in a variety of dried flower and pre-rolled formats.

name: Northern Lights
description: The famous Northern Lights is a pure indica strain rated at medium strength. Why so famous? This strain has multiple versions from all over the world but remains fairly common in taste and appearance. You will definitely feel relaxed while simtaneously happy. Like all indica strains, reommended for use in the evening or before bed. The flavours are pretty consistent with a tall Northern pine tree, earthy, piney, and slightly sweet.
description2: Royal HighÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Northern Lights is a pure indica. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s grown indoors on Vancouver Island with mother plants from imported seeds, and its honeydew melon flavour comes from the trans- and beta-caryophyllene, limonene, bisabolol and guaiol combination in its terpene profile. Northern Lights has medium THC potency and is available as dried flower in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g weights.

name: Quadra
description: Indica dominence in Quadra; however, a fairly well rounded strain in terms of effect. Moderate-high potency will help this strain produce both mind and body effects that are fairly long lasting. Depending on what your doing, expect to be highly focused while still relaxed and calm. Known to be worth the price, this strain will leave a zesty finish on your tongue without too strong of a smell.
description2: Quadra has frosty purple flowers and a funky Kush flavour with notes of mandarin zest, and its terpene mix includes beta- and trans-caryophyllene, limonene, terpineol and myrcene. This purple and white strain is hand-trimmed and hand-sorted, and has strong THC potency. It comes in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower sizes.

name: Red
description: Red is the fine wine of cannabis. This hybrid strain is not known to be sativa or indica dominant, producing a fairly balanced effect. It's medium strength will give you a desirable experience while #studying or #focusing. The best attribute of Red may just be the smell, a powerful earthy aroma that has its own soothing effect.
description2: Grown indoors and long-cured in Napanee, Ont., Fireside Red is a hybrid flower strain that is comparable to Spoetnik. It has medium THC potency and a robust terpene profile that includes myrcene and terpineol for an earthy aroma. Fireside Red is available in dried flower and pre-roll formats.

name: Reflect
description: Looking for a strain to help make your #runs or #hiking more interesting? Try Reflect for a bit of #motivation before #exercise. This hybrid strain is extremely potent yet balanced to ensure a great, long-lasting experience. The taste can be woodsy, spicy and peppery so its suitable for the more mature taste-buds.
description2: CoveÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Reflect is an indoor-grown hybrid strain with very strong THC potency. Its white and green buds are hand-trimmed and non-irradiated, and its aroma is earthy, woodsy, piney and peppery, thanks to the myrcene, alpha-pinene and beta-caryophyllene in its terpene profile. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in pre-rolls and three dried flower sizes (1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g).

name: Ease
description: A hybrid that leans sativa with balance in the THC:CBD ratio is the best way to describe Ease. This strain will offer a euphoric body buzz at a moderate intensity. A great choice if you're looking to tune out the noise and want to add a bit of solo #relaxation to your day.
description2: Ease is a sativa-dominant strain with mild THC potency. The large, airy and resin-rich green and yellow buds are grown and hang-dried in a hybrid greenhouse, and the citrusy, sweet taste and aroma are the products of a rich terpene profile that includes limonene, myrcene and nerolidol.

name: Rio Bravo
description: A high energy sativa strain, Rio Bravo is a great choice for a rockin' good time. Use this strain during the day for all sorts of #fun activities. You'll also get a really stronger flavour profile with hints of sweet and spice. Take this strain for a #walk and see for yourself.
description2: Sativa-dominant Rio Bravo from Edison is an indoor-grown and machine-trimmed strain featuring compact flowers laced with bright crimson pistils, and woodsy, spicy and sweet aromas from the terpinolene and myrcene in its terpene mix. It has strong THC potency and is available in four dried flower weights: 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g.

name: Sativa
description: The classic sativa strain. Everything we love about sativa including high energy, happiness, a bit of euphoria and just all around good mushy #feelings. The flavour can vary depending on the producer, but this will typically maintain a moderate strength and is ideal as a starting point to judge how different strains effect your personality.
description2: This greenhouse-grown sativa-dominant hybrid strain has very strong THC potency. Its buds stand out for their purple hue, and theyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re complemented by a sweet, earthy scent produced by the myrcene, alpha-pinene and beta-caryophyllene in its terpene profile. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in various dried flower sizes.

name: Serious Kush
description: Indica hybrid that comes from mixing the famous strains OG Kush and White Russian. Serious Kush is a modern approach to classic cannabis. Expect a fairly short high with a mild relaxation effect. This strain is high on quality with bold flavours of berries and spices, with a strong and soothing earthy aroma. As with most premium strains, the burn-out is fairly minimal so you can get away with using this in the late afternoon or after work.
description2: Serious Kush from Royal High is grown indoors on Vancouver Island with mother plants from imported seeds. This indica-dominant strain has medium THC potency, an earthy profile and a subtle, spicy finish. Its terpene mix includes alpha-pinene, beta-caryophyllene, humulene, limonene and myrcene, and it's available as dried flower in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g weights.

name: Super Sonic
description: Also known as Quantum Kush, Super Sonic is technically a hybrid but acts more like a sativa. Packing tons of horsepower, this strain may not be the best choice for beginner or even infrequent users. An extremely pungent odor and a somewhat harsh flavour profile prevent this strain from being widely adopted, but for some it might resemble an 18 year old single malt scotch.
description2: Super Sonic from Symbl is an indoor-grown sativa with fairly dense olive green buds with flecks of rusty red and a coating of frosty trichomes. Unlike most Kush breeds (which are indicas), thisÃ‚ Quantum KushÃ¢â‚¬â€œlike strainÃ‚ isÃ‚ a sativa-dominant hybridÃ‚ and hasÃ‚ a strong THC potency.Ã‚ Super SonicÃ‚ has a tropical taste andÃ‚ a complex and strong earthy yet sweet aroma. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in various dried flower sizes.

name: Temple
description: If you're looking to stimulate your mind, Temple may not be for you. This hybrid strain is very low in THC but packs tons of CBD. What does that mean? A great body buzz, usually used for medicinal reasons. You can still use Temple for a variety of reasons like #postworkout or #consistentsleep. Not the sweetest from a taste perspective, don't be suprised if you taste a bit of grape in the finish.
description2: Temple has a slight earthy odour and a mild, sweet, vaguely citrusy flavour. This hybrid strain has little to minimal THC potency and features a terpene mix that includes myrcene, beta-caryophyllene, guaiol and alpha-pinene. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s grown, machine-trimmed and hand-inspected in a hybrid greenhouse, free from pesticides and gamma irradiation, and is available in 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Balance
description: A hybrid strain that offers a mild dose of THC with much more CBD is what we call Balance. This strain will likely give you a shorter, less intense high but will have long-lasting effects on your body. Even though there is an indica dominence, this strain is known to be uplifting with heightened senses. Try Balance with some #music to mellow out and feel good. Last but not least, you'll love the spicy, smooth flavours.
description2: Balance from Solei is available pre-rolled and in many dried flower weights. Its dark green buds are sun-grown in a greenhouse and harvested at optimal times to ensure its signature spicy flavour, which comes from the peppery beta-caryophyllene in the strainÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s terpene profile. This hybrid has very mild THC potency.

name: Casablanca
description: REPEAT
description2: Indica-dominant Casablanca from Edison is a bold indoor-grown and machine-trimmed strain featuring plush, rich forest green flowers with hints of orange, tightly woven buds and an earthy, fresh aroma from the alpha-pinene and myrcene in its terpene mix. It has strong THC potency and is available in four dried flower weights: 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g. All Organigram products are individually packaged with Integra Boost technology, which preserves freshness and controls relative humidity levels, therefore extending the productsÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ shelf life.

name: CBD Shark Shock
description: A healthy mix of THC and CBD make this strain fun for everyone. CBD Shark Shock is a mild hybrid with bold flavours of fruits and citrus. Use this strain to get some #rest or just hang out on the couch being lazy. The effects can vary from person-to-person, but expect a subtle feeling of #joy with this strain.
description2: RedecanÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s CBD Shark Shock is a pairing of White Widow and Skunk #1. This strain, from OntarioÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Niagara region, has very mild THC potency and compact buds covered in resin. Its aroma is dank, fruity and sweet, and it tastes like green apple, sour citrus, sweet apricot and eucalyptus.

name: Galiano
description: Super strong sativa is the easiest way to explain Galiano. It will come on slow, but might give you the jitters if you have too much too fast. You should feel quite #uplifted, and because of the great quality here it's suitable for a wide range of users. Try this strain during the daytime for a little extra bounce in your step. Also, for all you mocha lovers, you'll really get a kick out of the smooth and subtle sweetness.
description2: Broken Coast's frosty, strongly textured Galiano buds feature a complex terpene profile that includes limonene, myrcene, caryophyllene and beta-pinene. Grounded by earthy, mocha notes and exhibiting a subtle natural sweetness, the green buds have strong THC potency and are available in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Go
description: A high quality sativa strain, Go is a safe bet for anyone interested in a mid-day energy boost. Priced reasonably, you'll definitely get your moneys worth when you try Go. No particular flavours stand out here, but it will be smooth overall without an extremely powerful aroma. Go have a #goodtime.
description2: Go from Tokyo Smoke is a hang-dried sativa-dominant strain with very strong THC potency and a terpene profile that includes beta-pinene, beta- and trans-caryophyllene, and terpineol, which produce floral and citrus notes, and hints of spice. Grown in a hybrid greenhouse, its dense flowers are light green with orange and gold tones. It's available pre-rolled and in various dried flower sizes.

name: God Bud
description: God Bud suggests that a tropical taste is the only way to experience the utmost in relaxation and euphoria. This indica strain is well known, and has a medium to high potency. It might be best to set-up your hammock before you use this product, but we bet you'll be glad you did. Sometimes, this strain can even give you a bit of the giggles.
description2: God Bud from Redecan has resin-coated buds with an herbal, musky flavour combined with tropical fruit and undertones of berry, lavender and pine. The odour can be described as tropical, earthy and citrusy (a result of the caryophyllene-rich terpene profile). This green-and-white-coloured strain with medium THC potency is greenhouse-grown in pesticide-free natural lighting conditions, and then hang-dried, hand-trimmed, sterilized and inspected. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g dried flower sizes.

name: Harmonic
description: Mild THC and CBD give Harmonic an uplifting and simutaneously calming effect. This strain is sativa dominant, but plays with your body and mind so you'll end up getting the best of both worlds. Great for beginners or pros, Harmonic helps you get #social without being overwhelming. No specific tastes worth mentioning, other than a light earthiness.
description2: Harmonic from AltaVie is a sativa-dominant strain with significant CBD levels for balance and mild THC potency. Its green buds are grown indoors, hand-trimmed and hang-dried indoors, and the myrcene in its terpene mix is responsible for the earthiness in its taste and aroma. AltaVie offers it as capsules (30 per bottle), as well as in 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: No. 402 Blueberry Kush
description: A berrilicious indica strain, Blueberry Kush is a fantastic example of obviously good matches - Blueberry and OG Kush. All the relaxation you could want, combined with a robust feeling of #happiness, you can enjoy this strain in the evening and expect to be perfectly ready for bed at the end of the night.
description2: Haven St. grows and harvests its indica-dominant No. 402 Blueberry Kush indoors as an irradiated whole flower, and then hand-trims and hang-dries the green and purple buds. Its myrcene-forward terpene profile gives it earthy notes and a sweet aroma. This strain has mild THC potency and comes in a variety of dried flower and pre-rolled formats.

name: North Star CBD
description: North Star CBD may not exactly help you find your way home. This sativa strain is all about the CBD. Expect mostly a body buzz, and it might be a good idea to try this strain in a vaporizer to get the most out of it. An activity like #yoga or #meditation might just be the perfect way to enjoy your North Star CBD. A pleasent floral scent, combined with fruits and cloves will leave you in paradise while you enjoy this strain.
description2: AltaVieÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s North Star CBD is a sativa-dominant strain with little to minimal THC potency that is grown, hand-trimmed and hang-dried indoors. Its floral aroma comes from the alpha- and beta-pinene in its terpene mix, while the myrcene and limonene are responsible for the earth, fruit and clove notes. This strain is available in capsules (15 per bottle) and 1 g, 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower varieties.

name: Polar Kish
description: A strong indica-dominant strain at a great price, Polar Kish is a wonderful take on the classic Shiskaberry. A lot of THC potency helps make this strain quite strong and a fruity berry taste make it fun to smoke. Use this strain later in the evenings, but if used just before bed you might get too strong of a high to fall asleep quickly.
description2: Polar Kish is an indica-dominant hybrid with a fruity berry aroma and taste. With very strong THC potency, its buds are shades of purple. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s 100% hydroponic, hand-trimmed and hang-dried indoors. Its terpene profile includes beta- and trans-caryophyllene, nerolidol, guaiol and limonene, and it's available in 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g dried flower weights.

name: Purple Chitral
description: Purple Chitral originates all the way from Pakistan will definitely make you happy and relaxed. This indica strain also adds a bit of euphoria, and like other indica strains will help you sleep. Although it's a fairly strong strain, its pure indica genetics keep it from being over powering. Tastes have been known to include a caramel sweetness with a cheesy finish.
description2: Woodstock Purple Chitral has medium THC potency. The green buds on this indoor-grown indica-dominant strain are hand-trimmed and hang-dried, and its robust terpene mix includes myrcene, alpha- and beta-pinene, and guaiol. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in a 3.5 g dried flower size.

name: Shishkaberry
description: A highly popular strain known as Shishkaberry offers an initially uplifting experience even though it is a medium strength indica-dominant hybrid. This is a great strain for social settings, but eventually you'll wind up very burnt out as the high wears off. The flavaours are sweet and earthy with a little bit of berry in the background. Try this strain over a dinner party or with a few friends for a fun filled evening.
description2: Shiskaberry from Redecan is an indica-dominant strain with dense, spade-shaped dark olive green nugs, minty green leaves and furry dark amber hairs with a thick, frosty coating of white trichomes. Greenhouse-grown in the Niagara region, this strainÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s sweet, earthy-fresh aroma is a product of the beta- and trans-caryophyllene, myrcene, limonene and humulene in its terpene profile. It has medium THC potency and is available as 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g packages of dried flower.

name: Solar Power
description: A true hybrid with a great strength at a reasonable price. Solar Power is an all-around winner. If you're looking for a happy, energetic and giggly experience, this strain is for you. It's great during the day or night, and has a fantastic citrus flavour. You could spend all day with this strain.
description2: Solar Power by Symbl is a Sour KushÃ¢â‚¬â€œlike strain grownÃ‚ indoorsÃ‚ in Paris, Ont., thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s known for its dense green and yellow buds. This true hybrid smells of lemon and pine, with a taste that includes tangy citrus, earthy wood and hints of diesel, all created by a terpene profile that includes beta-pinene and limonene. It has very strong THC potency and is available in various dried flower sizes.

name: Wappa
description: Wappa delivers a lot of value for an indica dominant strain. It has a medium strength and is generally well liked by all levels of cannabis users. Relaxed and happy as with most indica strains plus a slight euphoria can be expected here. Interestingly, this strain doesn't have an intense burn-out, so give it a try early in the evening for a bit of relief. The flavour is a very intense fruity taste, and the aroma isn't overpowering.
description2: Wappa has large, solid flowers that taper from a broad base to a sharply pointed tip and have a strong yet sweet aroma that verges on skunkiness, both of which also come through in the caryophyllene-forward taste profile. This green-and-yellow-coloured indica-dominant strain with strong THC potency is greenhouse-grown in pesticide-free natural lighting conditions, and then hang-dried, hand-trimmed, sterilized and inspected. Wappa is available in 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g dried flower sizes.

name: White Shark
description: Take a ride on the wild side with this sativa-dominant hybrid strain - The White Shark. You'll get a lot of strength with the THC levels in this award winning strain. A combination of #relaxation and #uplifting effects, combined with an energy boost and euphoria, you almost get a little bit of everything here. The flavours are quite musky and earthy but there is a little bit of fruitiness in the mix.
description2: White Shark is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain with a myrcene-rich terpene profile that delivers an earthy, musky flavour with a hint of fruit. This green-and-amber-coloured strain has strong THC potency, and is greenhouse-grown in pesticide-free natural lighting conditions, and then hang-dried, hand-trimmed, sterilized and inspected. White Shark is available in 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g dried flower sizes.

name: White Widow
description: White Widow is well-known in the cannabis community and has been around for quite a while. An internationally crossed sativa-dominant hybrid; this strain will provide a heck of a lot of #happiness and #uplifting effects but is also known for #creativity.No fruitiness here, White Widow is described as an earthy, woody flavour and a subtle musky aroma.
description2: White Widow is ahybrid strain with very strong THC potency. Greenhouse-grown, its green and yellow buds return an earthy and woodsy taste profile, thanks to the alpha-pinene and myrcene in its terpene mix. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 1 g, 3.5 g, 7 g and 15 g dried flower varieties.

name: Kinky Kush
description: Kinky Kush might just end up making you feel #kinky. This indica-dominant hybrid is extremely potent and powerful. The price is a steal for this strain, offering some of the best value in the Canadian cannabis market. The flavour profile includes a smokiness that's fairly unique to this strain.
description2: Grown and hand-sorted in the Niagara Escarpment, Kinky Kush is a hybrid strain with very strong THC potency. Its terpene mix of myrcene, alpha-pinene, beta-caryophyllene, bisabolol and guaiol give it a strong and rich earthy, fruity smell. Kinky Kush is available pre-rolled and in three dried flower sizes.

name: BC Delahaze
description: A medium/strong sativa strain is found all over BC Delahaze. This hybrid is more on the sativa side of things, providing a huge energy boost and help with #creativity, #focus, and #relaxation. Use this during the day if you're looking to get the most of your strain. The price is very high, but the "high" is even higher. Mango and lemon notes give this strain the perfect flavour combination.
description2: Mango and citrus notes provide a sweet overtone to the earthy, spicy aromas in this hand-trimmed, hang-dried BC Delahaze from Flowr. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s a sativa-dominant green and orange strain with very strong THC potency and a terpene profile that includes alpha-pinene, myrcene, trans-caryophyllene, terpinene and nerolidol. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available pre-rolled and in 3.5 g and 7 g dried flower sizes.

name: Critical Super Silver Haze,
description: Critical Super Silver Haze is a super strong sativa. Tons of THC give this strain a heck of a lot of strength, enough for an #energetic burst with a #happy feeling. The price might be partly due to the intense flavours found here, tons and tons of citrus. As with most sativa strains, definitely better for day-time shinannigans.
description2: Critical Super Silver Haze is a purple-coloured sativa-dominant plant thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s densely coated with trichomes and has a slightly sweet and citrusy aroma, incense and mentholated wood notes and a hint of pungent varnish. This strain is grown indoors in B.C. by Canna Farms and features a terpene mix of linalool, beta- and trans-caryophyllene, limonene and myrcene. Critical Super Silver Haze has strong THC potency and is available as a 1 g pre-roll and a 3.5 g package of dried flower.

name: Rise
description: Rise is a sativa-dominant hybrid that can be described as a fairly strong strain with a wide range of #positive and #energizing effects. As the name suggests, this is a great morning strain to start your day with great vibes and a lot of productivity. It's got a strong fruity flavour that compliments a complete breakfast.
description2: Rise, by Toronto-native brand Tokyo Smoke, is a sativa-dominant hybrid which offers medium THC potency with little to no CBD content. The strain features a fresh herbaceous bouquet with sharp notes of pine derived from its main terpenes, Limonene and Linalool.

name: San Fernando Valley
description: San Fernando Valley is also called SFV OG. A California founded sativa hybrid strain helps keep you off the couch while making you feel great #uplifting and #energizing effects. It's a little bit stronger than a medium strength strain, but still super smooth. The sweet and citrusy SFV OG will definitely make you #hungry so pick out a great place for brunch and help yourself.
description2: San Fernando Valley from WeedMD is a sativa-dominant strain with a terpene mix of beta-caryophyllene, nerolidol, limonene, linalool and beta-pinene. It has strong THC potency and is grown in a southern Ontario hybrid greenhouse. San Fernando Valley is available in a 3.5 g package of dried flower.

name: Bali Kush
description: A little bit of Bubba Kush mixed with Black Afghani and you'll end up in Bali? Bali Kush packs some serious strength for an indica-dominant hybrid strain. Potentially the best value in the OCS, this sweet strain will keep your appetite low, but still give you all of the great relaxing effects of an indica.
description2: Bali Kush is a purple and green indica-dominant strain grown and hand-sorted in the Niagara Escarpment. It has very strong THC potency, and an earthy scent with musky, sweet overtones that come from its terpene mix of myrcene, beta-caryophyllene, bisabolol, humulene and limonene. Bali Kush is available pre-rolled and in three dried flower sizes.

name: Easy Cheesy
description: Uniquely named Easy Cheesy is a sativa dominant hybrid with a strong kick. Try this strain towards the end of your day as you might still be able to stay #productive while bringing on the calming effects you love. It's a great strain for flavour with sharp cheddar and tangy notes.
description2: Easy Cheesy is a sativa-dominant strain with green buds thatÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s grown and hand-sorted in the Niagara Escarpment. It has very strong THC potency, and its terpene mix (myrcene, pinene, guaiol and limonene) contributes to the extra-old cheddar, musky, earthy aroma. Easy Cheesy is available pre-rolled and in three dried flower sizes.

name: THC Indica Aces
description: The Aces line comes in both sativa and indica varieties. For the indica, a great balance of THC and CBD give you a really cool mind and body buzz that end up making you super sleepy (not before you're super happy). This strain isn't usually smoked for the flavour, but rather the strength and ability to remain #functional.
description2: This indica pre-roll pack has very strong THC potency, and its terpene profile includes alpha-pinene, myrcene, terpineol and guaiol.

name: THC Sativa Aces
description: Sativa Aces is the second of two strain in the Aces lineup. This strain is known for a fairly high strength and a great #recreational experience. A great all-day variety, this pure sativa can be combined with all sorts of fun outdoor activities on a sunny day. Expect to smile.
description2: This sativa pre-roll pack has very strong THC potency, and its terpene profile includes alpha-pinene, myrcene, terpineol and guaiol.

name: Saturday Night
description: What are you looking for on your Saturday Night? If you want to jump into a #party, or just give yourself a great #uplift, try out the Saturday Night sativa dominant strain. You'll get a bit of CBD here as well so you'll get the mind, body and soul going at the same time. Not a lot of comment on flavour, lack of anything particular noteworthy in that area.
description2: Saturday Night has medium THC potency and a terpene mix that includes beta- and trans-caryophyllene, and limonene.

name: Elixir 1:1 MCT Oil Oral Spray
description2: Hexo's 1:1 MCT Oil Oral Spray comes in a childproof spray bottle. This fully activated sublingual oil with muted cannabis terpenes has mild THC potency. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s made with MCT oil, without the use of synthetic insecticides or pesticides. Each 15 ml bottle yields about 150 mists. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s also available in peppermint flavour.

name: Fleur de Lune Intimate Spray
description2: HexoÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Fleur de Lune THC-infused oil for intimate use comes in a spray bottle. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s formulated using a proprietary CO2 extraction of a greenhouse-grown hybrid strain and has mild THC potency. The terpenes in the fully activated oil are muted to remove the aroma. Each 30 ml bottle yields about 300 mists.

name: Reign Drops - 30:0
description2: With a 30:0 ratio of THC to CBD, Reign Drops by Redecan is a blend of greenhouse-grown cannabis with a strong THC potency. Formulated in Niagara, Ontario, this oil is put through a state-of-the-art ethanol extraction process and diluted to optimal concentration. Reign Drops is available in a 40 ml bottle. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are meant for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: Ace Valley CBD Pre-Roll Pack 1.5 g
description2: FlowrÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Ace Valley CBD is an indoor-grown hybrid from the Okanagan Valley in B.C. It has a purple colouring with a thick layer of orange, red and blue hairs, very mild THC potency and an earthy taste with fruity undertones created by the myrcene, trans-caryophyllene, alpha-pinene, terpinene and nerolidol in its terpene profile. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s hand-trimmed, hang-dried and available as 3.5 g, and 7 g of dried flower.

name: Rest
description2: Rest from Cove is an indoor-grown indica-dominant strain with strong THC potency. Its pink and green buds are hand-trimmed and non-irradiated, and its terpene profile, featuring limonene and linalool, returns a mix of citrusy, earthy and vanilla flavours. It's available in three dried flower sizes and pre-rolls.

name: 1:1 Capsules
description2: The oil in liivÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s vegan cannabis oil capsules is extracted using CO2 extraction technology. The greenhouse-grown hybrid strain used in the oil has a myrcene, beta-caryophyllene, linalool, humulene and limonene terpene mix, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s combined with grape seed oil and modified palm kernel oil to deliver a consistent 1:1 THC to CBD ratio. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 15-capsule bottles and has very mild THC potency.

name: Earth Oil
description2: Irisa Earth Oil is a blended formulation with a 3:5 ratio of THC to CBD, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s made with the ethanol extraction method. The terpenes have been removed from this oil, which has very mild THC potency. It comes in 30 ml bottles, and the indoor-grown strain is also available in pre-rolled packs of three. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: Highlands Softgels 10 mg
description2: Highlands cannabis softgels are made with CO2 extract from a greenhouse-grown indica-dominant hybrid strain with Afghan ancestry, and are formulated with non-GMO liquid coconut oil, gelatin and glycerine. They have mild THC potency, and theyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢re available in 15- and 60-capsule bottles.

name: Moon Oil
description2: Irisa Moon Oil is a terpene-free oil with very mild THC potency. This indoor-grown strain is made using the ethanol extraction method. It comes in 30 ml bottles, and is also available in pre-rolled packs of three. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: Penelope Softgels 2.5 mg
description2: Penelope cannabis softgels are made with CO2 extract from a hybrid strain (grown in a hybrid greenhouse) and formulated with non-GMO liquid coconut oil, gelatin and glycerine. They have very mild THC potency and are available in 15- and 60-capsule bottles.

name: Sativa Oil
description2: The THC in EdisonÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s Sativa Oil is ethanol-extracted from indoor-grown sativa-dominant cannabis, and is formulated with organic sunflower oil. It features beta-caryophyllene in its terpene profile for a spicy, woodsy taste. The oil has mild THC potency and comes in 25 ml bottles. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: Stars Oil
description2: Irisa Stars Oil is a blended formulation with a 4:3 ratio of THC to CBD, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s made with the ethanol extraction method. The terpenes have been removed from this oil, which has very mild THC potency. It comes in 30 ml bottles, and the indoor-grown strain is also available as a massage oil and in pre-rolled packs of three. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: Sun Oil
description2: Irisa Sun Oil is a blended formulation with a 3:13 ratio of THC to CBD, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s made with the ethanol extraction method. The terpenes have been removed from this oil, which has very mild THC potency. It comes in 30 ml bottles, and the indoor-grown strain is also available in pre-rolled packs of three. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.

name: THC Capsules
description2: The oil in liivÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s THC vegan cannabis oil capsules is extracted using CO2 extraction technology. The greenhouse-grown hybrid strain used in the oil has a beta-caryophyllene, humulene, linalool and limonene terpene mix, and itÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s combined with grape seed oil and modified palm kernel oil. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 15-capsule bottles and has mild THC potency.

name: Unplug Oil
description2: The Solei Unplug cannabis this oil is made with is sun-grown in an eco-friendly greenhouse. The oil has mild THC potency, and its terpenes have been removed. ItÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s available in 30 ml bottles. All oil products sold at OCS.ca are for ingestion only. DO NOT smoke or vape these oils. Use as directed.
